{"tid":1564784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"仆街黨鐵擬聘前啹喀兵任特遣隊","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:05:08.000Z","uid":117130,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8b58dbf9640b4e8992fe761249b3ed8286ba7a6b","tid":1564784,"uid":117130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:53:14.000Z","msg":"港澳新聞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">修例風波：車站頻遭破壞　港鐵擬聘前啹喀兵任特遣隊</span><br />\n<br />\n09月13日(五) 08:23更新 00:01建立 <br />\n<br />\n反對修訂《逃犯條例》抗爭持續三個月，港鐵車站設施屢受破壞，估計損失及維修費用高達數千萬元。港鐵行政總裁金澤培直言，現時港鐵正面對「前所未有、四十年來一遇的挑戰」，不但前線職員處理各衝突倍感壓力，車站設施持續被大肆破壞更險連累車站不能正常運作。金指正研究為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>港鐵保安人員加裝隨身錄影機拍攝</strong></span>各種破壞行為，更計劃<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聘請一隊「特遣隊」專責執行附例，對象包括前「啹喀兵」</span></span></strong>，認為尼泊爾人不諳廣東話，遭人以粗口「問候」時情緒較難被牽動，能減低衝突機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190913/bkn-20190913000136206-0913_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190913%2Fbkn-20190913000136206-0913_00822_001.html&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=a4b848cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190913/bkn-20190913000136206-0913_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3cf72c522bb817b91a4d27d1cf79e7f980e7cf83","tid":1564784,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=7e2df833\